    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justification. NIH predictions agree with FDA benchmark experimental data within 14.3% across all five operating points, satisfying the 20% acceptance criterion. RH < 1 confirmed for worst-case operating condition. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the specified COU.",
